                                  java.util.function.Supplier<java.util.function.BiFunction<Buffer,​BufferAllocator,​Buffer>> deframerSupplier,
                                  BufferAllocator allocator)
        Create a new instance.
        Parameters:
        deserializer - The Deserializer to deserialize each individual item.
        deframerSupplier - Provides a Function for each subscribe which is invoked each time a Buffer arrives. The Function is expected to return the a Buffer with enough data that the Deserializer can deserialize, or null if there isn't enough data.
        allocator - Used to allocate Buffers to aggregate data across deserialization calls if necessary.
